creator: Pavel Ilyin
descriptionHtml: Test your knowledge and the countries of the world. Memorize flags and capitals to complete all levels and become an expert in geography.
descriptionShort: Educational game about the countries of the world

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
— The ability to view the full list of knowledge for each individual country has been added to the knowledge screen. Click on the country to see the full knowledge.
— Added first achievements. There will be even more of them in the future.
— Work has begun on the new regime. In this mode, you will have to show knowledge of the borders of different countries.
